LINK GIA TH XRHSH TOY 'CRON' SCHEDULER KAI TH XRHSH THS 'AT':
http://www.ibm.com/developerworks/library/l-job-scheduling/index.html

EPIPLEON GIA TON 'CRON' SCHEDULER: 
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cron

PARADEIGMA CRON POY KANAME STO MAUHMA -: NA EKTELEITAI TO SCRIPT 'myjobs' 
EPANALHPTIKA KATHE 1 LEPTO -: PREPEI NA GRAPSOUME MIA GRAMMH STO CRONATAB 
ARXEIO MAS, THS MORFHS (ME THN ENTOLH 'crontab -e'):

0-59 * * * * /home/mamalis/myjobs

H AN THELOYME NA EKTELEITAI KATHE 15 TOY MHNA STIS 5 kai 20 TO APOGEYMA:

20 17 15 * * /home/mamalis/myjobs

PARADEIGMA AT POY KANAME STO MAUHMA -: AN THELOUME NA EKTELESOYME TO 
SCRIPT 'myjobs' stis 17 Dekembriou stis 3 kai 15:

at -f /home/mamalis/myjobs 15:15 Dec 17 2012

GIA NA DOUME POIES ERGASIES MAS EXOYME PROGRAMMATISEI ME CRON:

crontab -l 

GIA NA DOUME POIES ERGASIES MAS EXOYME PROGRAMMATISEI ME AT:

at -l

